description: Export a Hub repo as a HuggingFace-compatible directory (model.safetensors + config.json) using flodl's own writer. Auto-detects family (bert/roberta/distilbert/xlm-roberta/albert/deberta-v2).

# Argv forwards to the Rust example binary (entry: commands forward argv;
# run: commands do not — see feedback_cli_docs_three_contexts).
#
# First invocation compiles the `export_hf` example into the dev
# container's target cache; subsequent invocations are instant.
#
# `compile: true` opts the cargo entry into schema probing: fdl runs
# `<entry> --fdl-schema` once on `-h`, caches the JSON, and renders
# help from it on every subsequent invocation. Pays the compile cost
# on first run; invariant after.

docker: dev
compile: true
entry: cargo run --release --manifest-path /workspace/flodl-hf/Cargo.toml --example export_hf --features hub --
